<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You've Been Assigned to a Shift</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0e2f52; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .email-container { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ed956, #0987c9); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content p { color: #5a6c7d; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        .content p strong { color: #0e2f52; }
        .shift-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #7ed956; }
        .shift-card h2 { margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #0e2f52; font-size: 20px; }
        .shift-details { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; }
        .shift-detail { flex: 1; min-width: 120px; }
        .shift-detail .label { font-size: 12px; color: #5a6c7d; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .shift-detail .value { font-size: 18px; color: #0e2f52; font-weight: 600; }
        .shift-detail .value.time { color: #0987c9; }
        .location-box { background: #e0f2fe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .location-box .label { font-size: 12px; color: #0369a1; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .location-box .value { color: #0369a1; font-size: 14px; }
        .info-box { background: #dcfce7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 25px; }
        .info-box p { margin: 0; color: #166534; font-size: 14px; }
        .btn-container { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.3); }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .footer p { margin: 0; color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer .brand { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Shift Assigned!</h1>
            <p>You've been scheduled for a shift</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= studentName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Great news! You've been assigned to a shift for the following event:</p>

            <div class="shift-card">
                <h2><%= eventTitle %></h2>
                <div class="shift-details">
                    <div class="shift-detail">
                        <div class="label">Date</div>
                        <div class="value"><%= shiftDate %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="shift-detail">
                        <div class="label">Time</div>
                        <div class="value time"><%= shiftStartTime %> - <%= shiftEndTime %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% if (eventLocation) { %>
                <div class="location-box">
                    <div class="label">Location</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= eventLocation %></div>
                </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p>Please make sure to arrive on time. If you can no longer attend this shift, please contact the organizer as soon as possible.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="btn">View in Dashboard</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="brand">Volunteens</span> - Connecting young volunteers with opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
